  + [periphery] is source evidence, tests, outside markers, frame reference, balance center
  + [boundary] is codex owns execution; packet remains guidance until output target compiled attention packet SOP record is produced and reviewed
  + [outside] is hidden model state, unvalidated scaffold optimization, automatic worker launch, proof beyond cited sources
  + [depth] is slender
  + [gates] is source_preservation, outside_preservation, balance_check, frame_reference_check, validation_check, codex_review
  + [expected_output] is compiled attention packet SOP record
  + [balance_score] is stable
  + [balance_alert] is none
  + [frame_reference_integrity] is not_required
  + [rail_junctions] is capture_job_need, select_scaffold_profile, bind_boundary_and_outside, check_balance, check_frame_reference, emit_packet
  + [source_refs] is .sop/platform/AttentionScaffoldCompiler.sop, .sop/platform/AttentionBalanceCenter.sop, .sop/platform/FrameReferenceIntegrity.sop

